title: The Aguenar Tamanrasset (DAAT) airport in Algeria is available for Microsoft Flight Simulator (MSFS)
description:
In this video, we will delve into the latest addition to MSFS: Aguenar Tamanrasset (DAAT). Located in the southern region of Algeria, this airport serves both military and commercial purposes. To my knowledge, it is the first airport in Algeria to be released.

For a full overview of items added to the marketplace this week have a look at the video below:
